rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey Saika.
I just had a thought...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0002
rows.name: Oh no.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0003
rows.name:
Don't be so quick to judge! You don't
even know what I'm going to say!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0004
rows.name:
Well you're not the most sophisticated
of thinkers. I can read you like a book.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0005
rows.name:
Hey, you can't talk to your
Driver like that!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0006
rows.name:
Go on then. If I'm so easy to
read, what am I thinking?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0007
rows.name:
You ARE that easy to read and you just
came up with a new title for yourself.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0008
rows.name: Uh...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0009
rows.name: Haha, bingo.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0010
rows.name:
You are sooo predictable.
Go on then, what is it this time?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0011
rows.name:
I promise not to laugh.
You can tell your older sister.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0012
rows.name:
Older sister? ...Wait a sec! What makes you
think it'll be something to laugh at?!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0013
rows.name:
Listen, when I tell you my new title,
you're gonna be proper impressed.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0014
rows.name:
Zeke B Ultimate Genbu,
CHAOTIC Bringer of Chaos!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0015
rows.name: *snort*

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0016
rows.name:
Oi!
I heard that!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0017
rows.name:
You can't deny the coolness
of the name, surely!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0018
rows.name:
Of course not. It's very cool. Suits
you down to a tee. Super cool.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0019
rows.name:
You're not even pretending to
be serious! Why don't you try again?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0020
rows.name:
*giggle*
It's so funny watching you guys.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0021
rows.name:
Oh, Homura!
You arrived at just the right time.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0022
rows.name:
We're getting nowhere with Saika.
Homura, lend us your judgment.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0023
rows.name: Who, me?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0024
rows.name: Yes, you! What do you think?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0025
rows.name:
Zeke B Ultimate Genbu,
Chaotic Bringer of Chaos!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0026
rows.name: What DO I think?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0027
rows.name: That's a fantastic name!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0028
rows.name: Honestly, it's kind of goofy.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0101
rows.name:
Right? Obviously!
I knew you'd know what's what.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0102
rows.name:
Sorry Homura, but you really don't have to 
worry about His Highness, you know?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0103
rows.name:
I am being honest!
I think it's a very creative name.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0104
rows.name:
Eh?
No way... You're kidding, right?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0105
rows.name:
Man, it's such a relief to have 
someone who really gets it!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0106
rows.name: Go on, Homura! You need a title as well.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0107
rows.name: Huh? Me?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0108
rows.name:
Yes! Something that really captures
the spirit of who you are.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0109
rows.name:
Steady on, My Prince.
Homura doesn't want a stupid name.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0110
rows.name:
Please, Zeke-san!!
Give me that title!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0111
rows.name: Someone's gotten carried away...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0112
rows.name:
Right then. From now on, Homura,
you shall be...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0113
rows.name:
Homura F Super Ultimate Radiance! 
What do you think?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0114
rows.name: Homura F Super Ultimate Radiance?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0115
rows.name:
Uhh, really Homura... If you don't like it,
you shoulda just said so.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0116
rows.name: I love it!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0117
rows.name:
To be honest, I don't really know what
it's supposed to mean. But it's so cool!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0118
rows.name:
What on Alst is going on?
These two are incorrigible.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0119
rows.name:
Right? Just like I thought.
Homura GETS me.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0120
rows.name:
In fact, maybe YOU should
just be my Blade!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0121
rows.name: A-ah...I think I'm good, thanks.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0122
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0123
rows.name:
You're very amusing, Zeke-san, but Drivers
need to be a lot more than amusing.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0124
rows.name: What?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0125
rows.name:
Ahahaha! You're going to
need an Ice Art for that burn.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0126
rows.name:
That was worth the wait. It's gonna
take him some time to recover.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0201
rows.name: And it's redundant as well.

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0202
rows.name: Urk...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0203
rows.name: My Prince?!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0204
rows.name:
Too...too blunt. It struck me...
right to my very heart...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0205
rows.name:
Hang in there! It's just a flesh wound!
You're going to be just fine!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0206
rows.name:
Huh?
Is Zeke-san OK?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0207
rows.name: No... Remember me well, friends...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0208
rows.name:
What?!
I-I'm so sorry! I didn't mean-

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0209
rows.name:
I just let my thoughts spill out
of my mouth without thinking!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0210
rows.name: *cough*

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0211
rows.name: My Prince?!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0212
rows.name:
Um, what's happening?
I, er, should I get help?

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0213
rows.name:
Homura, no! 
The prince is gonna lose it if you keep this up!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0214
rows.name: Who knew Homura could be so savage...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0215
rows.name:
That wasn't my intention at all!
I'm sorry!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0216
rows.name:
I just thought that the joke
wasn't up to your usual standard...

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0217
rows.name: Ahck!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0218
rows.name: My Prince?!

rows.label: kizunatalk044_msg0219
rows.name:
A mortal blow. It's going to take him
some time to recover from that...
